description: Sexy, muscular Axel Kane and his wife’s assistant boyish, athletic Will Braun have been having a secret affair. Dark-haired Axel decided to head over to the office to see his wife, but she wasn’t having it and asked him to leave. However, instead of leaving he decided he might as well get a piece of Will’s sweet bottom since his wife rarely gives him any.
title: Tricky Tricks Part 2
